{"title":"关于长征","authors":["肖红"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":6,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于长征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肖红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于长征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我所感受到的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是红色岁月最悲壮的部分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是旷古空前的艰苦历程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一队叫做夸父的先辈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们握别瑞金握别洪湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握别娇妻与乡亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着太阳的足迹追寻光明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举着穿满弹洞的红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逶迤向北如长缨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这支队伍衣衫褴褛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疲倦流血并且饥寒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从苦难中生出坚强性格"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨难与艰辛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨不掉不屈的天性"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从血泪中走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向理想走去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这群执著而自信的先辈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过草地和雪山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前仆后继浩气如虹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史一开始就认定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是中华民族史上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要永远保留的章节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的被花朵包围的各种故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在历史与现实之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长成一个世纪的根基"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让整整几代人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这根基上吸取营养"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生根开花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结出红色果实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我常在远离长征的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感受这段历程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深刻体会我与这段历程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的血缘关系"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先辈的血液、沉淀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一脉相承为我的血性"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接过种子誓言和枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从历史的回音中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吸取执著和坚韧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热爱真理守护爱情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用终生的赤诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强化责任"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}